@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Animal Liberation ";
}

<h1 class="my-4 text-center">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p style="text-align: center;">
    The HEAL Foundation visited the many animal organizations and are always delighted to spend time, walking and petting many furry friends. The biggest concern is providing food, shelter and to bring awareness to these organizations who provide a voice for the voiceless.
</p>

